I want to study social work. I want to help children who are hurt or not taken care of. I also want to help families who are having problems. My values for social work are:

- Help others
- Respect people
- Do the right thing
- Work to improve relationships between people
- Keep learning and staying good at my job

These values are important for social workers and for me personally.

I have always wanted to help others. But I was not sure what job to do. In high school and college, I saw many people run away from their problems. Some people used bad ways to deal with their problems. I decided to study Psychology. After I finished college, I took a break. One summer, I visited a friend who had a 16-year-old boy on her couch. He was very nervous. My friend told me he was running away from his parents. The next day, he called the police. I went to his house to see if I could help. I talked to the police and told them I had a degree in Psychology. The police asked me to talk to the parents. They were nervous and said their son was being "bad" for asking for help. After that, I decided to study social work to help children with family problems.

Another value for social work is fairness. We say that every person is important, but we often try to be like everyone else. I am an individual and I like to be myself. I want to stand up against unfairness. In high school and college, I stood up against unfairness whenever I could. I wore what I wanted, I listened to the music I liked, I stood up against racism and discrimination. I believe in fairness and I will keep standing up for what is right.

This paper looks at two models. These models are about insomnia. The first model is called the biological model. It looks at genetics and health. The biological model says that some people may have a problem with sleep because of what they inherit. It also says that medical problems can cause sleep disorders.

The second model is called the sociocultural model. It looks at how the environment affects sleep. This includes things like a person's race, ethnicity, demographics, and economic status. This review will look at these two models and explain the research that is related to them.

There are different kinds of sleep disorders. These include sleep disorders that are a primary problem, sleep disorders that are related to another mental health problem, and sleep disorders caused by medical problems or substance use. Primary sleep disorders are called Dyssonmias and Parasomnias. Dyssonmias include insomnia and hypersomnia. Insomnia is when a person has trouble sleeping. Hypersomnia is when a person has trouble staying awake. Narcolepsy is another Dyssomnia. It involves problems with cataplexy and automatic REM.

The sociocultural model looks at how environment affects sleep. It includes factors like a person's race, ethnicity, demographics, and economic status. This review focuses on insomnia and primary sleep disorders in relation to the biological and sociocultural models.

The biological model of sleep disorders looks at genetics, heritable factors, and how our bodies control sleep. A part of the brain called the hypothalamus helps control sleep and wakefulness. This study used mice to learn more about how sleep works. The study found that a special molecule called orexin helps control sleep and wakefulness. If this molecule is activated, it promotes sleep. If it is not activated, it causes anxiety and helps the person sleep. The study also found that a medicine called baclofen can help increase sleep time.

The sociocultural implication of this study is that genetics can play a role in sleep. If a person inherits a problem with sleep, it can affect their daily life. This can make it hard for them to do things like go to school or work.

This paper looks at three parts of Central Auditory Processing Disorder (CAPD). First, CAPD is explained. Next, how to diagnose the disorder is explained. Finally, the paper says how a teacher can help a student with CAPD in a regular classroom.

CAPD is a problem that affects how our brain uses sound. It means our brain cannot hear clearly. People with CAPD can hear normally, but their brain has trouble separating sounds. It is not a hearing problem. They can hear, but they have trouble understanding what they hear.

CAPD was first known as "auditory imperception" in the 1950s. Researchers were studying children with communication problems. They started to make tests for these children in 1954. A scientist named Kimura came up with a way to test how our brain hears two sounds at the same time in 1961.

CAPD can cause many problems. A person with CAPD may have trouble finding where a sound is coming from. They may have trouble telling two sounds apart. They may not be able to recognize patterns in sounds. They may not be able to tell when someone is being sarcastic. One sound may be blocked by another sound. They may not be able to understand what they hear.

To diagnose CAPD, a doctor or other expert must test the person. They will watch how they listen and do tests. The tests may include questionnaires, observing how they react to sounds, or looking at how they do on tests that check their hearing skills. There is no one test that works for everyone. There is no known cause for CAPD. The tests may give the person many sounds at the same time and ask them to choose the right one.

A teacher can help a student with CAPD by being patient and understanding. They can ask the student to repeat what they say. They can use visual aids, like pictures or gestures, to help the student understand. They can also give the student more time to answer questions.

The play Twelfth Night teaches us that pretending to be someone else can be helpful in some ways. But it can also be very hard to stop pretending and be yourself again. If you lie too much, you may lose your friends and family. You have to decide if you want to save yourself or your relationships with others. Some people will not be very upset if they find out they were tricked. But others will be very angry.

Deception in Twelfth Night is especially complicated when men and women switch roles. This makes many other problems. One big problem is, why do people want to pretend to be the opposite sex? In the play, Viola pretends to be a man to protect herself. She is afraid of being hurt by men in a new country. Her plan works, but it makes her not have friends who are women. This is sad, because women can be very helpful.

Viola is very good at pretending to be a man. But it causes problems. Olivia, a woman in the play, falls in love with Viola. She thinks Viola is a man. This is confusing for Viola. Viola also has feelings for Orsino, a man in the play. But she must pretend to be a man, so she cannot tell him how she feels.

Some readers think that Twelfth Night shows how pretending can help people understand their true feelings. For example, Olivia and Orsino may really like each other, but they do not know it. Viola's disguise helps them see their true feelings. But Olivia is not really in love with Viola. She is just playing a joke. When Olivia meets Sebastian, she falls in love with him. This makes it clear that Olivia is not really in love with Viola.

The German colonial government was very cruel. This is especially true for the Ovaherero and Nama people in German South West Africa. The German colonial government made many rules and had different ways of ruling different places. The way they taught people to read and write was also different in different places. 

When the British took control of German East Africa in 1919, they found many African people who could read and write. The German government did a good job teaching people in Kamerun and other colonies. 

But things were very different in South West Africa, now called Namibia. In East Africa, the government built schools and helped teach the local people. In South West Africa, the government left teaching mostly to missionaries who did not get much help from the government. The government did spend a lot of money on schools for European people in the colony. This created a big difference in education between European and African people. Many people in South West Africa remained uneducated and unable to read and write. 

Many things caused these differences. This paper will look at these things and study the thoughts of European settlers and colonial leaders about African people. 

There are many books about education in the German colonies. Most books are in German and were written a long time ago. These books mainly talk about the education system in different colonies. Later books in English compared education in different colonies and looked at specific parts of the education system. These books showed that education was very different in different colonies. 

One important book is by Cohen, who studied education in South West Africa and East Africa. Cohen said the main reason for the difference in education was the number of European settlers in South West Africa. 

South West Africa has a good climate. But most of the land is desert. Many European people lived in South West Africa because it was a good place to live. By 1913, almost 15,000 European people lived there. This was a lot more than in East Africa, where only 5,336 European people lived.

The classification of popular music has grown very big over the last 100 years. There are now many different kinds of music, and it is hard to name them all. Most kinds of music have smaller kinds within them. For example, rock music has many kinds, such as heavy metal.

Heavy metal has become a very diverse and expressive kind of music. It shows a wide range of feelings, mostly on the darker side. People started to make their own kinds of heavy metal music soon after it began. They were able to create new kinds and sub-kinds of music because heavy metal is very flexible.

Now, there are many different kinds of heavy metal groups. It is hard to say what heavy metal really is. Heavy metal has taken ideas from other kinds of music, but it started from somewhere. To understand heavy metal music today, you need to know what it is and why it is a movement.

Heavy metal is a movement that is defined by darkness. It is a kind of music that has more volume, more energy, and more emotion. People who play heavy metal music are very good at their instruments. Heavy metal music is also related to the use of drugs. In the 1970s, people used drugs that made them feel crazy, and they created music that was very different.

Heavy metal has dark and emotional qualities that were new to music at the time. It also took some ideas from the Romantic Era, which was known for its dark and emotional music. Many lyrics in heavy metal songs express the darker side of the movement. One example is a song called "Helter Skelter" by the Beatles. This song is considered one of the first heavy metal songs. It was a response to another song by the Rolling Stones that was also very heavy and dark. The Beatles wanted to show that they could make heavy music too.

Henri Rousseau was a famous painter. He made dreamlike pictures. His 1910 painting, The Dream, shows a woman in a dream place. It also shows Rousseau's own dreams and wishes. He wanted to be famous and have people like his art. But he had a big problem. He wanted to be accepted by the art world, but he was worried about being different.

Before we can understand The Dream, we need to know about Rousseau's life. He was born on May 21, 1844, in a town in northwest France. His father was a man who sold metal things. Rousseau grew up without learning art. He worked for the government until he was 40. He was called a douanier, or a customs inspector. His first wife and eight babies died. He was very sad and had one daughter left. He started painting to feel better.

Rousseau was not like other artists of his time. He painted about the life of ordinary people. He wanted to be accepted by the art world, but he had a problem. He was not educated in art, and he started painting late in life. Many famous artists were already famous when Rousseau began to paint. He did not get famous until around the same time that another artist, Matisse, was becoming well-known. Matisse and Rousseau were different. Matisse painted because he did not want to make boring pictures. Rousseau painted because he wanted to make pictures that were safe and normal so people would like them.

Many people think that ethics and beauty are closely related. I think they are connected at a basic level. John Keats says in a famous poem, "Beauty is truth and truth is beauty." We learn many things in life, but we like things that are beautiful and good without being taught. We try to explain why something is beautiful or good, but we cannot make a list of rules for all good art and good behavior.

Critics of art or behavior can never fully explain what is good or beautiful. People talk about famous paintings, like the Mona Lisa. They discuss the colors, the background, and the context. But in the end, these things do not explain why the painting is good. When people talk about their favorite art or literature, they often say "there's just something about it" before explaining more.

I think that art and ethics cannot be fully explained. No matter how much we describe a work of literature, there is something special that is not explained. This is also true for ethics. It is hard to explain why something is good or right. A famous philosopher, Ludwig Wittgenstein, says that ethics cannot be expressed and it is beyond explanation.

I think that ethics and art are closely related because we experience them at a deep level. They affect us in a way that is hard to explain. This connection is even stronger with literature. Literature is special because it has a moral quality. It helps us understand what is right and wrong.

[Literature is like living. It involves values. We find values in literature that help us understand life.]

Germany is a strong country today. It is a united country with its own special culture. This culture comes from many different places. It is seen in the city of München, where the Alps are, all the way to the city of Kiel, near the Baltic Sea.

German culture is also seen in Köln, on the Rhine River. It is found in the center of Germany and in the city of Dresden, on the Elbe River. This special culture comes from many different groups and tribes.

Germany's ancestors were the Germanic people. The name "Germany" comes from an old word. Scholars and historians do not agree on the exact meaning of the word.

The Roman historian Tacitus wrote about the Germanic people in 98 AD. He said they were a separate group of people who did not mix with others. They came from ships, not from other lands. Who would leave a warm place like Rome to go to a cold place like Germany?

The Romans went to Germany to get goods and to fight battles. They did not live in Germany. They stayed in Rome and ruled their big empire. The Germanic tribes lived on the borders of the Roman Empire. They traded goods and fought with the Romans.

The name "Germany" may come from a tool used in battle. It may come from a word that means "to shout". The Germanic people were loud and noisy.

In the past, the Roman historian Tacitus wrote about the origins of the Germanic people. He said they were a special group of people who were not mixed with others. They came from ships, not from other lands.

I looked down.  The view was very interesting.  My mind was empty.  I was thinking, but I was not thinking about what I was seeing.  My thoughts came and went quickly.  I was very aware of what I was looking at.  Everything seemed easy and simple.  It was like my mind was not really thinking.  It was just experiencing what I was seeing.

I once read a book called "The New Drawing on the Right Side of the Brain".  An artist friend told me to read it.  I wanted to learn to draw when I was six years old.  The book teaches how to draw.  It says to draw a square around the thing you want to draw.  This makes a complicated picture easy to see.  For example, a bowl of fruit on a table in a kitchen becomes a simple picture on a flat surface.

At that moment, I could not draw a square around the picture in my mind.  I was very surprised and amazed.  I stood there and looked at the bowl.  Pablo Picasso liked the color blue, Claude Monet liked green, and Italian artists liked many colors.  If I wanted to be an artist, this was my chance to start.  I called my picture "Work in Brown".

I picked up my pencil.  My muscles relaxed and tightened.  I was ready to create.  Water and other things moved smoothly.  Then my hand knocked on the toilet handle again.  The brown thing would not move.  It was stuck.

I held a mop in my hand.  My feet were apart.  I wore a green tie.  I looked at the dirty brown thing in the toilet.  It was ugly.  Someone had left it for the people who clean the bathrooms at Rite Aid.  I stared at it for a while.  Then I moved my hand to the toilet paper and wrapped it around it.  I was holding it tightly.

I stood up straight and bent down.  My hand went slowly into the bowl.  It was like a mother putting a turkey in the oven.

Teenagers are dying in car crashes. Many reasons cause this problem. One reason is that the teen brain is not ready for the dangers of driving. Teenagers do not have enough experience behind the wheel. This lack of experience causes more accidents and more serious problems, such as cars rolling over, driving too fast, and crashing off the road.

Teenagers also drive badly when they are with their friends. A study in California showed that the more young passengers, the more car accidents. California and other states try to make driving safer for teens by giving them special licenses that limit the hours they can drive and do not allow other minors as passengers.

But these special licenses are not a complete solution. The real problem is that young drivers are not good at handling risks and responsibilities. Psychologist Marvin Zuckerman says 18 is too young for a regular driver's license. He found that many people under 20 like to take risks for fun. This is why we should delay driving until they are older. If we continue to give licenses to young teens, many more accidents will happen and the death toll will be very high.

By 2010, many more teens will be able to drive. If we do not change the laws, many more will die. A simple law can solve this problem. Schools can teach driver's education classes, but no one under 18 can drive a car. A special permit can still be given before a full license, and teens must practice driving with an adult for a certain number of hours. This will help keep teens safe. The law I suggest is not new.

I looked through the Library of Congress's early films made by Thomas Edison. I chose to watch fifteen films made from 1895 to 1901. These films use tricks to create illusions. My study of these tricks focused on the artistic rules for most trick films and how some later films were different.

Most trick films from this time period are shot on a set in a special place where you sit. The camera does not move to follow people or objects. This style comes from theater and magic shows. One problem with this style is that people in the films usually only move side to side and do not walk towards or away from the camera. An example is a film called Uncle Josh in a Spooky Hotel (1900). The actors enter from one side and move back and forth.

The way the camera takes pictures also does not change much. The camera usually takes long shots, and sometimes medium shots. Close-up shots are never used in these early films. This is because the theater and magic shows do not use close-up shots. The actors do not go towards the camera, so close-up shots are not needed.

Most early trick films are short, usually less than one minute. This is because they are made from a few short pictures that are joined together. The films usually show simple tricks, like magic or disappearing acts, and do not have a long story. However, some films are not as simple. For example, The Execution of Mary, Queen of Scots (1895) is a trick film that looks like one shot, but is actually several shots joined together.

John Taylor was a strong supporter of the Republican Party.  He was a farmer, but his work in politics made him known for speaking his mind.  He believed in freedom and thought that the government should not control people too much.  Taylor thought that farmers were very important to society and that their work should be protected.

The United States was a new country.  It did not have old customs to follow.  This meant that the country's leaders could create a fair system of government.  Taylor believed that all people have natural rights.  These rights are important and should not be controlled by the government.  He thought that a fair society would not allow strong people to take advantage of weak ones.

Taylor believed that a good government must consider both good and bad things about people.  He thought that governments are run by people and that people are good and bad.  Good principles in a government protect people's property, help farmers, and do not allow too much richness.  A good government will be fair, even if its leaders are not.

Taylor wanted the government to be very small and have only the powers listed in the Constitution.  He thought that a big government would be expensive and might be cruel.  However, he also thought that a simple, literal interpretation of the Constitution could be dangerous.  Taylor thought the Declaration of Independence was more important than the Constitution.  It tells us that the United States is a group of independent states, not just one country.

Looking at the graph, we see a big drop in commuter log submissions in the third month. This was bad news. We do not know why it happened. One reason could be the winter weather. Fewer people ride bikes or walk to campus in winter. Also, it is the end of the school year. Students are busy finishing their schoolwork. They may forget to keep their log. December is the holiday season. Many students and teachers do not need to come to campus. They take a long break. 

In January, students go back to school. But the number of log submissions is still small. This may be because the project was exciting at the beginning. People get less interested as time goes on. To stop this, we had a special week in March called Carpool Challenge Week. We gave away prizes to encourage people to participate. This worked. More people kept their logs in March.

The problem is that people like driving their cars. They like being free and independent. To get them to use other ways to commute, we need to give them good reasons. We gave prizes like gift cards. But we could have done better. We could have given away a new bike, a new car, or a car that uses little gasoline. This could have helped more people participate.

The prizes we gave did not change much during the project. If we had given bigger prizes, maybe participation would have stayed high. We could have given bigger prizes in December, and even bigger prizes in January. This might have kept people interested.

An ETF is a special investment.  It is like a mix of many things.  It tracks an index, a commodity or a group of assets.  This mix is similar to an index fund but it can change easily, like a stock on a market.

An ETF gives you the benefits of many investments and the freedom to buy and sell quickly.  But it also has some problems.  You have to pay a fee for every trade, just like buying a stock.  On the other hand, the fees for ETFs are lower than for many other investments.

There are many types of ETFs to choose from.  But before choosing, it is smart to check if the benefits are real.  We are looking at the ETF IHF and its top 10 investments.  We want to know if owning one ETF is like owning many different investments.

We are looking at the top 10 investments that make up 63.58% of the ETF.  These are the ones that make the ETF valuable.  We will use a chart to show how these 10 investments work.

The chart shows that if we own just the top 10 investments, we can get a 6.11% higher return.  This is a 16% increase!  The chart also shows that the risk of the top 10 investments is lower than the risk of the ETF.

But we need to be sure that these results are real.  So we will look at how much each investment goes up and down.  This is called the standard deviation.  We will compare the standard deviation of the top 10 investments to the standard deviation of the ETF.

One of Edgar Allan Poe's famous poems is "Dream-Land". Poe says this poem is one of his best. In "Dream-Land", Poe uses the word "Thulé" twice. The word "Thulé" comes from Virgil, an old writer. Virgil used the word to describe an island north of Britain, which the ancient Greeks thought was the end of the world.

Poe liked the work of German writers. One of these writers is Goethe. Goethe is famous for a long poem called "Faust". In "Faust", there is a short poem called "The King of Thulé". This poem is about a king who loses his wife and starts drinking. He then decides to die.

Poe's poem "Dream-Land" and Goethe's poem "The King of Thulé" are similar. They both describe a king who is very sad. Goethe's poem was written many years before Poe's. But Poe might have seen it in a book. "Dream-Land" and "The King of Thulé" can be read together.

Poe also mentioned "ultma Thule" in another poem called "The Pit and the Pendulum". "Dream-Land" is a good example of how Poe was influenced by Goethe's work. Goethe was a well-known writer, and Poe would have known him. Poe admired another writer, Tennyson. Poe said he liked Tennyson's work. Poe would have also read Goethe's work because many of his books were printed again after they were first published.

A customer fell and was hurt when she slipped on applesauce in a store. The store's manager, Paul Martin, was told of the spill twice. He did not clean it up because he was eating dinner. Can the customer get extra money from the store for this? 

A judge will not quickly say no to the customer's request for extra money. To get extra money, the customer must show that the store manager acted very badly. The customer must show that the manager knew his actions would cause harm. 

The customer will say that Martin should have cleaned the spill because many other people slipped and fell in the store before. The customer's friends were hurt in the store in the months before she fell. Martin still did not clean the spill. 

The customer will argue that Martin's actions were very bad. This is because many people fell in the store and Martin did not take care to keep the store safe. 

On October 13, 2009, an employee told Martin about the applesauce spill. Martin said he did not have time to deal with customer complaints. Later, another employee also told Martin about the spill. Martin said the same thing: he did not have time. At 5:30 pm, the customer slipped and fell. Before she fell, five other people had slipped and fallen in the store that year.

The customer is suing the store for her injury. We are looking at whether to ask the judge to stop the customer from getting extra money.

In California, a person can get extra money from someone if they acted badly. The person must act with "oppression, fraud or malice." The law says "malice" is when someone means to cause harm. If they do not mean to cause harm, they must act very badly and not care about the safety of others. A court said a person acts badly when they know something will cause harm and they do nothing to stop it.

Four years ago, I took a class about Islam at a school.  We talked a lot about whether Islam is a religion of violence.  I think this question is more important now than ever.  After 9/11, I saw the news change.  They used to say bad things about Islam, but now they say good things.  In 2001, it would have been hard to imagine a president like Barack Obama, who has a Muslim family background.

I read the biography of the Prophet Muhammad.  This book is interesting to me.  It says Muhammad was a kind and humble person.  But I thought he was different.  I thought he forced people to join Islam.  He would conquer cities and make people change their religion.  But the biography says he was a martyr who was misunderstood.  People came to believe in him because they thought he was telling the truth.

There are some strange similarities between the lives of Jesus and Muhammad.  For example, Muhammad multiplied food and drink for many people.  This makes me think the writers wanted to show Muhammad as a humble man who did not need to prove himself.  This is a problem because it takes away from the miracle of Jesus' life.

I also did not like some of the stories in the biography.  They are like second-hand stories.  Someone tells you something they heard from someone else.  This makes the stories seem not true.  I think the writers wanted to show that people converted to Islam on their own.  But it looks like they are making it up.

What bothers me most is that the writers make Muhammad look like a perfect man.  But history says he was not kind and humble.  I wonder if Muslims know the real story of how he became powerful.

The ideas of Jesus and his views are not followed by many Christians today.  But if we look at the history of Christianity, we see a change over time.  Many Christian ideas are different from what Jesus taught.  This is because Christianity changed after Jesus' death.  But today, people are becoming more aware of this change.  They want to know what Jesus really taught, not what others added to his ideas.

Some people still believe in the old ways.  They will not accept new thoughts.  But these people are not the majority.  In the future, more people will understand the past.  They will want to know what Jesus really said and what he meant.  It may take many years, but this will happen.  Then, people will go back to Jesus' ideas.  They will remove the extra ideas that were added.  The church will still be strong, but its ideas will be the same as they were a long time ago.  Christians will think and act alike.  They will be more alike than different.

This has happened before in history.  The Romans persecuted Christians, but later they became Christians.  Our country went from treating African-Americans badly to giving them important jobs.  The same thing will happen in the Christian church.  People will look back to Jesus' ideas.  They will understand his words are not always meant to be taken literally.

Jesus lived a long time ago.  Before that, the Jewish people believed in one God.  They thought God spoke to them.  They believed in the Jewish holy book.  But the Jewish people were not all the same.  They were different groups like Sadducees and Pharisees.

I think The Jungle shows people are naturally selfish. They only think about themselves and want to make their lives better. But they do not care about others. The Jungle shows this in many ways. The owners of big companies only think about making more money and making their companies bigger. They do not care about anything that gets in the way or gets hurt. 

The writer, Upton Sinclair, describes a big factory like this: "The line of the buildings stood clear against the sky." He is showing the damage that pollution from the factory is causing. The owners do not care about people or animals that get hurt because of their company. They do not care about the pollution from the factory or the dirty water from animal pens.

The owners also do not care about their workers. They work the workers very hard so they can get rich. "All places are bad. There is no loyalty." The owners force the workers to work very long hours and may fire them without a warning. There were few laws to protect workers in that time. The owners could do what they wanted. The workers had to work in bad conditions and live in bad areas. There were no organizations to help them. Some workers joined groups called unions, but these groups often made money from the poor workers. The workers were very unhappy and had no way to escape the bad system of Packingtown. They were treated like slaves. "Many people are very poor. They can barely eat. They depend on the owners for work. The owners are very mean."

Many writers use different ways to make readers feel a certain way about important things. Some of these ways are more effective than others. F. Scott Fitzgerald uses many of these ways in his book The Great Gatsby. Fitzgerald pairs words that do not usually fit together to give readers a feeling. He uses this technique with colors. He makes colors mean something. Then he uses these meanings to remind readers of a feeling.

Fitzgerald builds up meaning for white and gray in his book. White means something better and higher class. Gray means older and faded. He uses these meanings to show readers a feeling. He does this at the beginning of the book. He shows people always wearing white. Daisy and Jordan are always wearing white. People are always wearing white at parties. Only when Nick is describing Gatsby's party are people not wearing white.

Fitzgerald makes white and gray more clear by using them with common things. He says people's names are gray on Nick's schedule. He says a place is a white house in a row of houses. He says some people and places are white or gray. He describes Jordan and Daisy as having a white childhood. He says there are gray cars and gray land in a valley. He says a dog-seller is a gray old man.

After Fitzgerald makes white and gray mean something, he uses them to show readers that some people or things are not important. He starts with Daisy. He does not use white and gray for a long time. Then he describes Daisy as wearing white. Readers see Daisy as not a special person, but as something Gatsby wants.

Fitzgerald uses this technique with Daisy many times to show readers that she is not special. He says Daisy's fur has a gray haze. He says she wears white again before Tom and Gatsby meet.

San Diego County is a good place for growing food. The climate is mild and sunny. This makes it easy to grow many kinds of food. Tomatoes, citrus fruits, leafy greens, squash, broccoli, herbs, peaches, lemons, berries, and peppers are some of the food grown here. Many people want to buy organic food from local farms. These farms give tours and allow people to walk and watch birds. This can help the landowner get money from the government and make the land better for animals.

Organic farming is good for the environment. It has more plants and animals because it does not use bad chemicals. But, it can be more expensive. It needs more work to remove bad insects and weeds, and to make the soil rich in nutrients. A small farm like this cannot produce as much food as a big farm. It also costs more to plant special crops to help the environment. 

The land I chose is in the San Diego area. It is near the town of Potrero and the Cleveland National Forest. Many animals live here, including some that are in danger of disappearing. The government has a plan to protect them. The land has been used for many years for grazing and making wood. I looked at government programs that can help a small farmer. I also found an example of an organic farm in the same area.

Culture plays a big role in all negotiations. But what is culture? Culture is not the same for everyone. It is not one thing. Culture is different in different places. We should not say all people from a country are the same. For example, saying "all Russians are stubborn" is not true. We need to understand the culture of a country and how it affects negotiations.

When we talk to people from another culture, we compare them to our own culture. This can help us understand their culture. But we should not judge another culture. We should accept it as it is. We should work with the culture, not against it. This is especially true when we are in a weaker position in a negotiation.

If we are in a foreign country or working with a different company, we should respect their traditions and beliefs. This can help us overcome cultural barriers and move the negotiation forward.

Culture is not just about countries. Companies have their own culture too. A company might work very long hours or have a more relaxed schedule. We can see a company's culture in how employees dress, how they communicate, and how they hire people. Some companies help their employees help other people, while others do not.

Values are important to understand. They tell us why people behave in certain ways. If a culture values saving face, a person will not talk badly about their company or boss to get what they want. If a culture values a strong bargain, a person will not settle easily. We should think about these values before we start negotiating. But it is also important to learn about the person we are negotiating with, so we can work together effectively.

A man said, "There is no God." This is from the Bible, in Psalm 14. St. Anselm used this idea in his argument about God. Thomas Aquinas also believed this. Their ideas are similar, so we will compare them. We must assume they are both right about God to make this comparison. If we think of a different kind of God, we cannot compare their ideas. We need to start with the idea of the God in the Bible.

We will compare St. Anselm's idea first. Anselm said we can find God by looking inside ourselves. He said we cannot imagine that God does not exist. This means the proof for God is in our minds. Anselm thought we do not need outside help to know God. We can find truth about God by looking inside ourselves. This idea is called faith. Faith is trusting in something without proof.

St. Thomas Aquinas had a different idea. He said we can prove God exists with reason and facts. We do not need faith. This is good for spreading Christianity. It helps people join the church because they can use logic to understand. Aquinas used five different ideas to prove God: change, why things happen, when things happen by chance, how good things are, and harmony. He said God is necessary for these things to be true. If you have a puzzle and know all the other pieces, you can know what the missing piece is.

A long time ago, around 2500 years, a prince was born. He would later be called Buddha. He gave up his life in the world and became very wise. His teachings led to the creation of Buddhism. The most important kind of Buddhism is Theravada Buddhism.

Buddhism is an old religion. It is different now from when Buddha lived. You can see this in the country of Sri Lanka. Every year, they have a special ceremony. Many people, including monks and laymen, take part in this ceremony. This ceremony is important to them, but Buddha never taught about such a celebration. These differences are not just small ones. They go from simple traditions to the basic ideas of the religion.

The Theravada Buddhist community has changed its important ideas over time. This is because of both external and internal forces. External forces come from non-Buddhists. Internal forces come from Buddhists themselves.

Now, let's talk about some special terms. An internal force is something that comes from inside the Buddhist community. An external force comes from outside the community. A hostile force is anything that harms or tries to harm the Buddhists. A benign force is something that does not want to hurt or help the Buddhists, but may do one of them by accident.

We need to understand the basics of Theravada Buddhism. Buddhists find comfort in three things: the Buddha, the Dhamma, and the Sangha. The Dhamma is made up of three baskets of Buddhist text. The Sutta Pitaka has many teachings, the Vinaya Pitaka has rules for how to live, and the Abhidhamma Pitaka has ideas about the world.

Important ideas in Buddhism include Anatta (there is no permanent self), Dukkha (life is suffering), and Anicca (everything changes). By understanding these ideas, we can end Sansara (the cycle of death and rebirth). We can also stop lobha (desire), dosa (hatred), and moha (delusion) when we become enlightened.

In the Vinaya Pitaka, there are rules for how to live. Laymen follow five simple rules: do not kill, do not lie, do not steal, do not have bad sex, and do not take drugs. Monks follow many more rules. The most important idea in Buddhism is the four noble truths. First, life is suffering. Second, attachment causes suffering. Third, suffering can be overcome.

The United States and Mexico had a big problem for 57 years. This problem started in 1836 and ended in 1893. It was a fight between the two countries. 

The biggest fight between the two countries was the Mexican-American War. It happened from 1846 to 1848. The United States won the war and got Texas and the Southwest as new land. Many other fights happened between the countries. But they stopped fighting before World War I.

The problem started because of disagreements about important things like religion and culture. The United States and Mexico also had different material interests. Many countries with a shared border have problems like this. 

The United States has problems with some of its neighbors. Mexico is one of them. David M. Pletcher said that only Mexico and Cuba have big problems with the United States. This is because they are close to the United States.

A problem with religion made things difficult between the two countries. Many people in the United States did not like Catholicism and the idea of a king. This was a problem throughout history. 

The United States and Mexico had many disputes. They lasted for 57 years. Most of the disputes were about land and people crossing the border. Bandits from Mexico and the United States caused problems. Both countries had to use their armies to control the border.

The problem started to end when Mexico became dependent on the United States. The United States wanted to help Mexico instead of taking its land. This was a big change in the late 1800s.

Fifteen years ago I became very sick. I was a nurse at the time. I chose this job because I wanted to be safe and have a steady life. Many people told me I would always have a job because people are always sick. They said I would be okay. But I wanted to be a scientist or a journalist. So I chose nursing.

Now I am 46 years old. I have no money. I am still very sick. I get Social Security money but it is not enough. Every day is hard for me. I am not sure about my life. But I know I would not be here without my family and friends. They help me a lot.

My point is that bad things can happen in life. We cannot be sure of anything. We must help each other. We must ask for help when we need it. We should trust each other.

In the United States, we put too much trust in the government. But I think it is better to trust each other. We should help our neighbors and friends. The people who built America a long time ago did not do it alone. They worked together and helped each other.

We should be prepared for bad things. I have a special kit for emergencies. It has food, water, and other things to keep us safe. If you have a farm and can grow your own food, that is great. But it is also important to know your neighbors.

People want to know why living things change over time. Are there rules that guide how they change? In 1917, a scientist named D'Arcy Thompson said that it is hard to describe the shapes of animals in simple language. This is still true today. Recently, scientists have been using math to understand how animals grow and evolve. Our study is trying to use math to understand how living things change over time and space.

We are studying a group of animals called Prunum. We are using X-ray pictures of these animals to find numbers that can help us model their shells. We used these numbers to make computer models of their shells. We are looking at how their shells could change over time. We are also doing experiments and observing the shells to understand how they evolve.

A shell is like a tube that turns around as the animal grows. This tube has many parts, called whorls. The whorls are like layers that spiral around a center line. This line is called the columella. The whorls get bigger at different speeds, and each whorl is separated by a line called a suture. The biggest whorl is the last one, called the body whorl. The other whorls are called the spire.

We can look at shells from different sides. There are four sides: apical, basal, apertural, and abapertural. The most common way to look at a shell is from the apertural side, with the opening facing us and the top pointing up.

To count the whorls, we look at the shell from the top and find the first line. We then draw a line to separate the shell into two parts. We count the whorls from this line, and we can even count a part of a whorl.

A shell is like a path that the animal follows as it grows. We can trace this path by looking at the center of each whorl and the size of the opening. We can use math to represent this path. This helps us understand how the animal's shell grows. We can then change the math to see how the shell could change over time.

Indonesia's numbers for infant and baby deaths have not changed much in the last 10 years.  The country is making progress on some goals like water and sanitation, but it is not making enough progress on health care for children and mothers.  This is a problem.

Indonesia has improved the number of births where a trained health worker is present.  Now 72% of births have a trained worker.  But this number includes traditional workers like midwives who cannot help during complicated births.  So, many mothers are still dying from heavy bleeding.  The progress in this area is not as good as it seems.  We also see that fewer children under five years old are getting medical help for diarrhea.  We do not have enough information on help for new mothers, but it is clear that this is another problem.

Fewer than 4% of babies are born by cesarean section.  This number is too low.  In cities, 7% of babies are born by cesarean section, but in villages, it is only 2%.  This shows that health services are not equally available everywhere.  The poor have less access to healthcare because they cannot pay for it.

To fix these problems, we need to decide how to make healthcare more available.  We can either make specific programs for specific problems or we can make the whole healthcare system better.  Program-specific approaches are attractive because they are easy to understand and give quick results.  But there are some problems with this.  When we invest a lot of money in one area, other areas may not get enough money.  Also, when we have many programs for one area, it can be confusing and wasteful.

Victorian novels are known for their careful details. They often focus on the aristocracy of that time. Two books that are different from this style are "Oliver Twist" and "Wuthering Heights". These novels use mystery and strange events to make the characters more interesting. This helps readers understand their feelings and reasons for acting a certain way.

"In his mind, many confusing ideas came together. He was still walking between two men who were angry. He could hear their words. When he looked up, he found he was talking to them. He was suddenly very scared. He heard guns and loud voices. He saw lights and was moved quickly away. He felt a lot of pain and was very unhappy."

(Dickens, 220)

These two books use mystery in different ways. Sometimes they use dreams or strange states of mind. In "Oliver Twist", these strange things help readers understand Oliver's feelings and what he is going through. When Oliver is shot, he remembers the event in a dream-like state. This shows that he has no control over what happens to him. He feels a lot of pain and is very scared. This makes the reader wonder who is responsible for his troubles. It seems it is not Oliver's fault. This event makes Oliver feel like he has lost control of his life. It also shows that he is giving up.

"The day was short. It came and went very quickly. It was quiet and then it was dark. The darkness was very long, but it seemed short because it was always changing."

I worked in an after-school program two years ago. I helped elementary students with their studies. I was good at English and reading. One boy, Adrian, had trouble reading. He was in third or fourth grade, I think. 

Adrian was very smart and could speak perfect English. But he had a problem: he did not know the English alphabet very well. I met his mother, who spoke only Spanish. We used simple words to talk. Then I understood Adrian's problem. He could read, but not well because he did not know the alphabet.

I tell this story to show a big problem: a language barrier in schools. Even a child who speaks good English can still have trouble reading. This problem exists everywhere, including in California. We need to solve it.

In Adrian's case, I helped him with English reading, especially the alphabet and pronunciation. But for other children who do not speak much English, the solution is more complicated. There is no one way to fix this problem. We need a combination of things: dual language systems, mainstream immersion, private tutors, and ESL classes.

The dual language system is a good idea. It helps all children, not just those who speak Spanish at home. Studies show that children in this kind of program do better in school. Some people are afraid it is a waste of money and that most children will not benefit. But that is not true. If we use this system in all classrooms, all children will benefit.

How do we make this work? Do we need all teachers to speak two languages? That would be difficult and not realistic. But we can have special helpers, like bilingual tutors or aids, to assist teachers.

Most people are told from a young age that something greater than themselves exists.  Some go to school to learn about it.  Others go to special meetings or look inside themselves for answers.  Many people accept the ideas their parents teach them.  But some people do not believe in these ideas.  They think there is no more to life than what we can know.  We all look for a guiding light to help us through dark times.

One day, I asked my father about his favorite bird.  We sat on the porch of our house.  It was raining and we were smoking.  I remembered my father's look.  He stared out into the rain.  I could tell he was thinking about something.  He had lost some weight.  His hair was thin.  I felt sad and alone.  I was afraid to talk to him about my feelings.  If I talked about it, it would be too real.  So I hugged him and sat back down.  We looked at the rain together.

My father died in December.  It was a few days after my birthday.  He was sick for a long time.  The doctors tried to help him, but it did not work.  I thought to myself, "What kind of person would do this?"  I did not pray.  If God was real, I thought, he was not listening to me. 

I did not want to see my father die.  I did not want to watch the person who created me leave this world.  I wanted to remember my father as he was, not as he died.  I knew my father better than anyone else.  I knew he would not have wanted me to watch him die.  I stayed in my bed for three days, waiting for the news.  But no one called me.

The Gothic Novel is a mix of old and new. This is what Ian Watt says in his book The Rise of the Gothic Novel. People have given the Gothic style many names - good and bad. Some say it is not deep, but others think it is powerful and beautiful (Burke). The first Gothic Novel, The Castle of Otranto, was written by Horace Walpole. He mixed old and new ideas together to create something new. Walpole used old theatrical ideas and new ways of writing to make a new kind of story called "A Gothic Story" (Walpole 4). The Gothic style uses old ideas from medieval theatre, buildings, and customs. When The Castle of Otranto was first published, the word "Gothic" was used to describe different people, styles, and times. At that time, people thought it was old-fashioned and not smart.

The combination of old and new is what makes the Gothic style last a long time. It is still new and old to readers who are far away in time from when the story was written. 

One idea that is very important in Gothic stories is chivalry. Chivalry is the way a knight is trained to be brave, honest, and skilled. This idea is used in the first Gothic Novel, The Castle of Otranto. Chivalry is important to Gothic writers because it represents a perfect knight who is brave, honest, and skilled. Writers like Walpole saw that society did not live up to this ideal. They used chivalry to make the past seem better than the present. Walpole wrote The Castle of Otranto during a time of trouble and was worried about the future. He may have thought that people in the past were better than people today.

In his story, Walpole shows this idea through a character named Frederic. Frederic is a prince who has suffered a lot. He is described as a brave, kind, and polite knight. This is an exaggeration, but it is also a way to show the importance of chivalry.

Supply chain management is a process of moving goods from order to customer. It includes getting raw materials, making products, and delivering them to the customer. This idea was created in 1982 by a man named Keith Oliver. He said that supply chain management is about planning, doing, and controlling all the steps in the process to meet customer needs quickly and well.

There are six important parts of a supply chain: production, supply, inventory, location, transportation, and information. Business managers use these parts to give good service to their customers.

Production is the first step. It is the base of the whole process. The production stage tells us when, why, where, and how to make things. Managers need to know what customers want. They look at the market to learn about customer needs. Once they understand customer needs, they decide what to make and how much to make.

Next, they decide where to make the products and which factory is best for good quality and amount. They think about customer needs and satisfaction. After that, they plan work and take care of equipment. Production is very important. Every detail matters. If details are not planned right, it can cost the company time and money in the long run.

For example, I worked at Wal-Mart and Target. Both companies have a plan for every part of their business. They have a plan for employee uniforms and for receiving goods from trucks. This helps the company work smoothly and without confusion.

The second important part is supply. Supply is about making good decisions about what a company can do well. A company may have many groups making the same product. The manager decides which group is best for each part of the product. They may also decide to work with other companies to make things faster and cheaper.

A manager might choose to work with other companies to be fast and flexible and to save costs.

A sign says Hitler is alive in Burma. Ellen Page holds it. She is a famous actor. Her sign is made of cardboard. The words are written with a marker.

Burma is a country in Southeast Asia. A group of strong men control it. They took power in 1962. They came to power by taking control of the government.

Many people in Burma are unhappy. They protest in the streets. This happened in 2007. Many monks were involved. They wore orange robes. The government was unhappy. They used force against the monks. Many people were hurt.

A Japanese journalist was killed in 2007. He was taking pictures of the protests. The government arrested many journalists. They did not want the world to know about the protests.

This is not new. Governments have been mean to their people for a long time. The Romans thought their leaders were gods. The Japanese thought their emperor was a god. Our country's president used to talk to a man who leads a group called the Republican Party. Some people think this man is not a good leader.

There have been many sad events. One was in China in 1989. Many students and workers protested against the government. The government did not like it. Many people died. We do not know how many. The Chinese government said 200-300 people died. Others said 2,000-3,000 people died.

Another sad event was in Rwanda. People killed each other. The government helped them. They killed many people because of their skin color. This happened in the 1990s.

Hitler killed many Jews in Germany. This was a long time ago. He thought they were bad people.

Duke Ellington is a famous jazz musician. He created many great works because he lived a long time. He had a special ability to create a good sound with his orchestra. Ellington played piano in many of his compositions, but he was an excellent composer. He wrote many pieces that showed the special skills of the band members. He made a plan for the band so the soloists could play freely. He also wrote tightly organized pieces that used the style of each band member. This helped to create a good sound for each piece. Ellington knew how to make the sound of each player and how they worked together. This helped him write some of the best jazz pieces in history.

The Grove Music dictionary talks about Ellington's sound and ideas. It mentions Creole Love Call, a piece where Ellington used voice like a musical instrument. This was early in his career. He used voice to add sound and color to his music without words. Creole Love Call shows how Ellington helped his soloists sound better. This is a slow, 12-bar blues piece with six parts. 

The six parts are:
Chorus 1: Ellington sang a smooth melody, then a rough sound at the end.
Chorus 2: A muted trumpet played a solo, adding to the melody and using long notes.
Chorus 3: A clarinet played high notes, with a piano playing a special rhythm.
Chorus 4: The full band played like the first chorus, with brass and reeds calling and responding.
Chorus 5: The reeds called and responded in a high register, with the brass and rhythm sections playing a special rhythm.
Chorus 6: The piece went back to the first chorus, with call and response between Ellington's voice and the reeds. The voice sounded like a growl, playing like a musical instrument.

In Creole Love Call, Ellington used his voice to add color to his music. This is just one way he made his music special. In Hot and Bothered, Ellington used his skill at organizing the band and his ear for sound. He combined a solo on muted trumpet with scat singing to make a rich sound. In It Don't Mean a Thing (If It Ain't Got That Swing), Ellington used a trombone to introduce the melody, showing his skill at using different sounds in his music.

She had always felt something was missing. This feeling would not go away. It started when she was 14. It was still there when she was 17. Now she wanted a person, not a thing. However, she did not like any boys. Some boys liked her, but she was not interested. She wondered why this was happening to her. She thought about it for a long time.

At home, life was usually peaceful. Her parents were good and calm people. They never argued. Her parents and she rarely argued. They argued about her being independent and free. Her parents were calm, but she was not. She had a fun and nice personality.

Today was not a peaceful day. She was looking for something new. She heard a loud cry from the kitchen. She ran in to see what was wrong. Her mother was on the floor and in pain. She said "Ow" over and over. Her daughter ran to her and helped her. "Mom, what's wrong?" she said. Her mother said, "I need you to take me to the hospital." Her daughter said, "Okay, Mom. Where is the hospital?" Her mother showed her the way. The daughter was happy she had taken classes to be strong. She carried her mother to the car and drove her.

The hospital was a scary place. There were bad smells and sick people. But she was not scared. She helped her mother and called for the doctors. The doctors came and helped her mother. A long time later, her mother was lying on a bed. They took her to be looked at. Her daughter was worried.

Her mother had fallen off a stool while trying to get a vase. She was trying to get something from a high cabinet.

This study wanted to show that eating a "Mediterranean Diet" is good for your heart. A high "alternate Mediterranean Diet" score means you are eating this kind of diet. The study found that people with a high score had a lower risk of heart disease and strokes.

The alternate Mediterranean Diet is like the Mediterranean Diet but with some changes. It has more plant foods, such as fruits, nuts, and whole grains. It also has more fish and less animal products and saturated fats. A little bit of alcohol is okay.

Previous studies showed that eating a Mediterranean Diet can help you live longer and lower your risk of heart disease. But these studies did not look at strokes.

This study followed 74,886 women from the age of 38 to 63. They were all nurses who were part of a big study. The researchers asked the nurses about their food choices six times from 1984 to 2004. They wanted to see what they ate over a year. About 95% of the nurses stayed in the study for 20 years.

The researchers used special questionnaires to ask about food choices. They checked the answers with medical records. If they could not find the answers in records, they said the case was "probable" and still counted it. They also asked about other things like weight, smoking, and exercise.

The researchers wanted to know how the women's diet changed over time. So, they took the average of the women's diet scores over two years. They also adjusted for things that could confuse the results, like age and smoking.

The researchers used a special method to see if a high diet score lowers the risk of heart disease and strokes. They looked at two types of heart disease and two types of strokes.

The study found that women who ate a lot of plant foods and fish had a lower risk of heart disease and strokes. Women with a high diet score had a 29% lower risk of heart disease and strokes compared to women with a low score.

In 2007, the United States had a very bad financial problem. Many people lost their jobs, and the value of homes fell greatly. Some of America's largest companies were also in trouble. The question is: how did this problem happen, and how can we stop it? Simply, the financial problem was caused by bad decisions by politicians who wanted to make people happy. They forced banks to give money to people who could not pay it back. The banks then sold these bad loans to others, which made the problem worse.

This problem began in 1999. The President at that time wanted to win a second term in office. He relaxed some rules to help people get home loans. This made things worse in the long run. A writer named Steven Holmes said in 1999, "Fannie Mae, a company that helps people get home loans, was being pushed to give loans to people with low incomes." Holmes thought that this would cause trouble in the future. He said, "The company may have problems if the economy gets bad."

Many things caused the problem to get worse. Some mortgages were not fixed, so the amount of money people paid each month could change. This made it hard for people to pay their loans. The government also created special loans that were not very safe. These loans were like a chain that connected many parts of the economy. When the housing market fell, many people lost money. The top five banks in the US had $4.1 trillion dollars in bad loans in 2007. This was 30% of the country's total money. In the end, some banks were sold or broken up, and others were put under close control by the government.

Exposition is a big problem for writers. It's when you tell too much in your story. This makes the reader bored or angry. Dr. Merlin often gets frustrated when she writes too much. 

You know the rule "Show, don't tell." But many writers still make this mistake. Exposition is like a bad influence. It says, "Tell the reader the history so we can move on." 

Exposition is when you tell the reader what happened. It's often boring and simple. In movies, one character often tells another a lot of information. In writing, the author does the telling.

Let's use an example. Imagine a story where the main character meets her husband. Then she learns he dies. But this can't happen in just two lines of dialogue. The story needs to show how the husband is a good person. This makes the reader care about him and the heroine. 

You want to know more about the husband and how he makes the heroine happy. This is called "meat on the bone." The story is just "They met, they married, he died." But you need to add more. 

As a writer, you must add the meat. Sometimes it's hard to write about some things. Maybe you have a new character and you want to tell a lot about him. But don't do it. Give the reader small clues about the character. 

For example, let's say he's a gas station manager. You can say, "He liked to fish." This is better than telling the reader everything about his past. Now the reader can imagine more.

I watched two news programs from Columbus, Ohio. The first one was live on NBC 4 on August 13, 2011. A man in Ashley, Ohio, named Shad Hostettler, stabbed his wife. They showed his picture. He looked very bad. The news spent two minutes on this story. They said he stabbed her many times and was arrested. I think they spent the right amount of time on this story.

The next story was about a young man named Travis Buyers, 18. He was shot in the Sharon Woods area. He is in the hospital in very bad shape. The police are trying to find the person who did this. They have not found a suspect yet. This story was short. I think it was short because the man was black and the neighborhood is also black. I have noticed that the news does not pay much attention to crimes against minorities. 

The news also talked about a hole in a medical helicopter. They said a small bullet hit the helicopter. They think it was shot with a small gun. The police are offering a five-thousand-dollar reward for information about the shooter.

The news also said there will be rain and thunderstorms on Saturday. The temperature will be in the middle to low eighties all weekend. They want you to stay tuned to hear more.

They also talked about a store robbery on Clime Road in Columbus. A black man with a black hoodie robbed the store. They said he is tall and weighs about 150 pounds. I think the news spent too much time saying he was black.

Another story was about a man named Rene Rodriguez. He is a convicted drug dealer. He was sent to prison for 25 years for selling marijuana from Texas to Ohio. I don't know why they said "300 months" instead of 25 years. They also said he is Hispanic, but that is not important to the story.

There is a special connection between brothers. This connection is strong and never breaks. Many feelings are in this connection, like love, pride, jealousy, and anger. Brothers understand each other more than anyone else. They see themselves in their brother. This connection is very clear when a situation is very bad. It shows if the connection is good or bad. When these feelings are clear, they bring a big price to pay. Understanding these feelings means dealing with the results they bring.

When one brother looks at another brother, they see themselves. They see themselves, not as others see them, but as they really are. Brothers show their true character in their actions and the results of those actions. 

In a story called "The Scarlet Ibis", two brothers explore this connection and the strong feelings that come with it. They live in a beautiful place. They go on a difficult journey. The brothers have big feelings of sadness and pride in a very important moment. Only one brother survives.

The story shows the brother's feelings through what they do and how they interact with each other. The narrator helps us see the brother's feelings and how they see the world. These feelings make the brother act in certain ways.

The brother's actions are led by one main feeling: pride. From the time they start going out together until the end, the brother feels unhappy with his little brother, Doodle. He wanted a brother who could do things with him, like holding his breath, running, and climbing trees. He wanted a brother who could play with him. But Doodle was very sick and couldn't do these things. The brother had big dreams, but they were crushed. He even thought about hurting Doodle. But when Doodle smiles, the brother feels happy. This shows that he loves Doodle in his heart. He had a strong love for his brother all along, but he didn't know it.

The brain is a very smart system. It helps us think and remember. Technology has improved a lot over time. So have the ways people describe the brain. A long time ago, it was like a piece of wax. Then it was like a piece of paper. Next, it was like a book. Today, it is like a computer.

The brain gets information from our senses. It changes sounds, sights, and feelings into signals. The brain uses these signals to make decisions. It does this by breaking down the information in two ways. First, it looks at the small parts. Then, it uses what it already knows to help it understand.

For example, when you look at a picture of a black box, the brain puts together small pieces of information like color and shape. It decides that you are seeing a box. The brain also uses what it already knows to help you identify the box.

The brain has a filter that decides what information is important. It helps you focus on what you need to see or hear. You might see many things, but your brain helps you choose what to pay attention to.

The brain also needs a place to store information. It stores different kinds of information, like what you see, what you hear, and what you remember. It stores this information in different ways. For example, it stores words based on how they look, how they sound, and what they mean.

The brain has different ways to keep information. Short-term memory, which lasts only a few seconds, is like a short message. Long-term memory is like a big library where information is stored for a long time.

Different scientists have different ideas about how the brain stores and uses information. Some think that it is like a big network with connections between ideas. For example, the word "chair" might be connected to the word "table," and the word "table" might be connected to the word "wooden."

Aldous Huxley writes a book called Brave New World. In this book, he says we should be careful about technology and the way people live under a system called capitalism. He creates a world where people value community above all else. They are taught to be happy and not to think too much from a young age. But the people in this world are not really in control. They are controlled by a person called the World Controller.

Huxley thinks that this system is not good. He uses a way of thinking called Marxism to explain why. Marxism is a way of looking at how people live and work together. Huxley uses words from Marxism, like "homogeny" and "reification", to show that he is concerned about the way people are living.

The book says that capitalism is not fair. People are fooled into thinking they are happy, but they are not really in control of their lives. This is called "false consciousness." It means that people do not know how they are really treated by those in power. In Brave New World, people are taught to want things they do not need. This is done through a type of sleep learning called hypnopædia.

The people in the lower classes do not know they are being tricked. They are happy to buy and consume things. The people in the upper classes know, but they do nothing to change the system. This is called "hegemony", which means that one group of people controls another group.

In Brave New World, people do not form close relationships with each other. The book says that this is because of technology and capitalism. People are not free to make their own choices. They are only interested in looking good and pleasing others. The book shows that people are happier when they are connected to each other and have their own thoughts and feelings.

The way people accept their place in society shows that capitalism is not fair. People are happy to do what they are told, as long as they get what they want. This is like the way Marx thought the poor would be fooled into thinking they were happy.

I have been a student at University Park for two and a half years. Getting around campus can be hard for many students, including myself. The freshman year, I was in an East Halls dorm room far from the center of campus. Classes were in buildings like Willard, near the center of campus. It took 25 minutes to walk from my dorm to class in bad weather. Someone who graduated not long ago told me that East Halls used to be far from other buildings. Now, there are sports fields and new buildings there.

The campus is getting bigger, so it is harder to walk around. A good solution to this problem is a bicycle. But just having a bike is not enough. Students must ride it, and the campus must be safe for bicycles. I talked to a friend who rides a bike. He said, "Bikes are good. It's the only way to get around." Bicycles are good for you and are fast. I live off campus, far from the center of campus. I have class in Thomas building, which is a 25-minute walk. My bike helps me. I can ride to class in 5 minutes if I go fast. The problem is that Pollock Road is not easy to ride on. I like my bike because I am busy. If I didn't have a bike, I would have to walk. Walking would take 30-40 minutes. That's over two hours a week. I don't have time for that.
